{"tid":1422025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派批評北京無限上綱　民間五大訴求與中央主權無關","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:48:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6d2e643e5f8c77cf94b726e32ec0fa4bd833ad","tid":1422025,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"昨日全港多區罷工、衝擊，國新辦開記者會譴責暴力，又指事件衝擊一國兩制。民主派批評，北京與特首林鄭月娥無限上綱上線，強調民間五大訴求與中央主權並無關係。<br />\n<br />\n民主派會議召集人毛孟靜指，她曾與參與運動的年輕人了解，「光復香港 時代革命」的口號，只是要求反暴力反黑，以及恢復香港高度自治。<br />\n<br />\n工黨張超雄批評林鄭月娥死不悔改，用警方暴力鎮壓，指示威者多番針對警署，是因為警方在處理示威活動時連番犯錯，甚至疑似與黑社會合作，反問這與國家主權有何關係。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄又指，民主派被人說成挾洋自重，但<span style=\"color: red;\">「稍有常識都知道，我們無力左右示威者，只能靠邊站」，形容抹黑民主派的人「睜大眼說大話」，目標是拉一派打一派。</span><br />\n<br />\n公民黨郭家麒指，國新辦發言人楊光在記者會指，中央繼續支持林鄭月娥管治，即是要延續林鄭的管治，已押注下去，形容決定相當不智。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒又批評，香港警察在721與元朗黑幫懷疑勾結，行為有問題，認為大陸再表明支持警隊的做法，<span style=\"color: red;\">「又行錯一步棋」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟范國威呼籲年輕人，不要隨便「送頭」，認為圍堵警署等行為危險，或會令運動轉弱。他提到，昨日全港大罷工，職工盟估計有35萬人參與，形容罷工很重要，「跨過香港歷史門檻」。<span style=\"color: red;\">他相信，大規模罷工比與警方硬碰的行動，可能是更是示威未來的出路。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yefgoGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyefgoGf.jpg&h=304043cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61168a3da1ef3a9b9913b59366cb328cedcc8f4e","tid":1422025,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:36:22.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b43c3dd83a19ce3fd0cdbe3a82cadeb14d46bb","tid":1422025,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n目的唔係分化p牌會員<br />\n而係當你見到有大量p牌洗正負評時<br />\n要比平時更小心去做決定"},{"pid":"20fb317daf637b670d28c4f8380deb764a208501","tid":1422025,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edae08b1fd52d69ca551d407aa5379d70d272275","tid":1422025,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />北京根本無知得可憐<br />\n搞到今時今日咁都唔知發生緊咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f722940a2e1faedb15c79e038d79313e8a2f4267","tid":1422025,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUkPJHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUkPJHD.jpg&h=d1dc750b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />煽動到比人tackle。"},{"pid":"3e0700fbcd9cbba4ab50a2b4050956a7a1400708","tid":1422025,"uid":271413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:40:44.000Z","msg":"做得好！"},{"pid":"91df1b28fa99e4f4dfba5403580a3a6293b49484","tid":1422025,"uid":177194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求"},{"pid":"8c13987432bd470ec9d0d21220aed2a0e2528a87","tid":1422025,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4345457cb90432997d1f1bf42a0de3af9bec9c75","tid":1422025,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6238149440de374ed98bdc8dd4aeae96a4285faf","tid":1422025,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:48: